        <mxCell id="Qqf6wXoDEP0wQ5kBnup_-47" value="&lt;h1&gt;Practical Example&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Bob wants to execute a given transaction (any valid DEMOS transaction). Its transaction instructs the RPC to use the IMP network when possible. All the workflow that is able to be channeled in the IMP will be executed, verified and computed off chain by using the same DEMOS trustless cryptography. Only the final, cryptographically secure result is then stored and attested on chain. The savings using IMP can reach 95% of the TX size.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="950" width="960" height="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
